The following parts of infermesh are copied verbatim or adapted from oMLX, with
the original SPDX-License-Identifier headers preserved on each file:

  * infermesh/api/                  — protocol adapters (OpenAI/Anthropic),
                                       request/response models, tool-call parsing,
                                       reasoning/thinking helpers, SSE formatting.
                                       Copied verbatim from oMLX omlx/api/, with
                                       imports re-rooted omlx.* -> infermesh.* and
                                       one mlx-only logits-processor class removed
                                       from thinking.py (unused without an MLX
                                       compute backend).
  * infermesh/core/pool.py          — multi-model pool orchestration (LRU
                                       eviction, pinning, TTL, leasing), adapted
                                       from oMLX omlx/engine_pool.py with its two
                                       mlx touchpoints (active-memory probe and
                                       executor helper) replaced by the
                                       hardware-neutral MemoryProbe and a
                                       core async-executor helper.

